text: SoleRebels enweela ọganihu, ma tolite nke inwe ndị ọrụ dị narị atọ n'ọnụ ọgụ na Ethiopia, na arụpụta ngwa ahịa a na-ekesa na mba iri atọ n'ụwa niile, na-eresi ndị na-eme ngwá nri Whole Foods, Urban Outfitters na Amazon. Ha nwekwara atụmatụ imeghe ụlọ ahịa ndị ụlọ ọrụ ya nwe na mba ndị dika Austria, Switzerland, Taiwan, na UK. Betlehem chọrọ ịmepụta ọrụ a na-akwụ ụgwọ nke ọma nke nwere ike ịmepụta ọganihu site na iji nkà ndị ọrụ aka na ihe ndị sitere n'ọnatarachi nke Etiopia. Echiche ịhọrọ akpụkpọ ụkwụ dị ka ngwaahịa mmalite nke ụlọ ọrụ ahụ bịara mgbe e mesịrị. Ihe cheere Bethlehem aka mgba mgbamume bụ seleate maọbụ ị kpọọ ya barabasso, nke bụ akpụkpọ ụkwụ e si na taya emegharịrị emegharị wee mepụta, nke a na-ejighi ngwá ọrụ ọgbaraọhụrụ mepụta na Etiopia, nke gụziri ya agụụ ime ka ihe ọ ga-arụpụta bụrụ nke ga-esi na akpụkpọ anụ.
question: Kedụ aha isi obodo  Etiopia?
answer: Addis Ababa

Campbell-Young jikọtara aka chọpụta ụdị ọhụrụ nke "Pearsonia" (Fabaceae) ma bipụta nchọpụta ahụ na 2008. [1]
question: Olee afọ Gael Jean Campbell-Young malitere ibi na mba Australia?
answer: Gael Jean Campbell-Young malitere ibi na mba Australia n'afọ 2007.

text: Ọ gara n'ihu na-arụ ọrụ ya na nyocha mpara akwukwo ma na-achụso ngalaba omumu di elu bu PhD na Mahadum Curtin [1] na mgbe oge nke njikwa nyocha na nkuzi agụmakwụkwọ tinyere ezumike nke ọ zụrụ na nka dị egwu, ọ tụgharịrị ọrụ ya n'ime njikwa Project nke ihe dị iche iche na ọrụ iji ala eme ihe. Kemgbe ọnwa Machị afọ 2020, e were ya n'ọrụ dị ka Project Officer - Short-Term Modular Housing Program for Bushfire Recovery Victoria, ngalaba nke gọọmentị steeti Victoria.

text: yaA mụrụ Carolina Jaume na 18 Ọktoba 1985 na obodo kachasị ukwuu nke Ecuador, Guayaquil, nne na nna ya bụ Rafael Jaume nke Puerto Rico na Diana Saporiti, onye bụbu onye na-emepụta ihe onyonyo si Ecuador. Jaume malitere n'oge na-eme ihe nkiri na TV, mana ọ hapụrụ n'oge ọ na-eto eto ruo mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na itoolu, mgbe ọ banyere n'asọmpi Queen of Guayaquil nke afọ 2004, a kpọrọ ya "Star of October". Jaume mere ihe nkiri mbụ ya na TV n'afọ 2006 na telenovela "Amores que matan" [es] nke Ecuavisa mepụtara na usoro "De 9 a 6", ebe ya na Xavier Pimentel [es], di ya n'ọdịnihu rụkọrọ ọrụ. N'afọ 2007, Jaume ga-amụ nwa nwanyị di na nwunye ahụ, mana alụmdi na nwunye ahụ kwụsịrị otu afọ mgbe e mesịrị, n'afọ 2009.

text: Deborah Owusu-Bonsu (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 25 n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1984) nke a maara nke ọma site na aha ya dị ka Sister Derby bụ onye na-eme ihe ngosi telivishọn nke Ghana, onye egwu na onye nlereanya nke Akan na onye na-eme ihe ngosi na e.tv Ghana.
question: Deborah Owusu-Bonsu osi ebee?
answer: Deborah Owusu-Bonsu si n'obodo Ghana.

text: Owusu-Bonsu egosila ọkachamara ya na mmasị ya maka ubi ọ họọrọ site n'ịrụ ọrụ nke ọma maka obere ụlọ ọrụ yana nnukwu ụlọ ọrụ na Ghana, United States na United Kingdom. N'afọ 2012, Owusu-Bonsu dekọrọ ma wepụta otu egwu (egwu) nke akpọrọ 'Uncle Obama' na-ezo aka na Barack Obama nke ụlọ ọrụ telivishọn United States CNN kpuchiri. Kemgbe afọ 2012, Owusu-Bonsu bụ onye na-ahụ maka mmemme "The Late Nite Celebrity Show" nke ụlọ ọrụ telivishọn e.tv Ghana na-agbasa. O mechakwara ga GHOne Television ebe ọ kwadoro ihe ngosi ya, "Gliterrati" maka obere oge tupu ọ nyefee Berla Mundi.
question: 'Uncle Obama' bu egwụ etiri na olee afọ?
answer: Etiri egwu 'Uncle Obama' n'afọ 2012.

text: Zahra Ben mime (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 30 n'ọnwa Septemba n'afọ 1988) bụ onye Iraq-Tunisian na-eme ihe nkiri, onye ngosi na onye nlereanya. A maara ya maka ọrụ ya na Hawa Baghdad .
question: Kedu ihe ejiri maara Zahra Ben bụ onye a mụrụ n'afọ 1988?
answer: Ihe ejiri maara Zahra Ben bụ ime ihe nkiri na egosi ihe nlereanya.

question: Gịnị kpatara Zahra Ben jiri bụrụ onye amama n'obodo?
answer: Ihe kpatara Zahra Ben jiri bụrụ onye amama n'obodo bụ na ọ na-eme ihe nkiri na egosi ihe nlereanya na Hawa Baghdad.

text: A mụrụ ya na Baghdad site na nna onye Tunisia si Sousse na nne Iraq si Al Diwaniyah . Ọ biri na Baghdad ruo mgbe ọ dị afọ isii wee soro nna ya kwaga Damaskọs na Siria ebe ọ biri afọ iri na atọ nke ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ ya. N'afọ 2007, ọ kwagara Tunisia ebe ọ malitere ọrụ ọkachamara ya.
question: Kedu n'afọ amụrụ Zahra Ben mime?
answer: A mụrụ Zahra Ben n'afọ 1988.

text: Ọrụ ngosi uwe ya malitere mgbe onye na-ese foto bụ Jean-Paul Goude chọpụtara ya, onye hụrụ ya ka ọ na-eje ije n'ụsọ osimiri mgbe ya na Carla Bruni na-agba mgbasa ozi "Club Med" na Bahamas. Goude tinyere Jnifen na mgbasa ozi ahụ ma nye ya aro ka ọ gaa Paris ma zute onye na-emepụta Azzedine Alaïa. Ọ ghọrọ ngwa ngwa ihe nlereanya kachasị amasị ọtụtụ n'ime ndị na-emepụta ihe na Europe, na-eme njem n'etiti Milan na Paris mgbe ọ na-arụ ọrụ maka Armani, Fendi, Jean Paul Gaultier, Roberto Cavalli, na ndị ọzọ. Ọrụ Jnifen na-aga nke ọma na ejiji agafeela afọ iri atọ na-anọchite anya ụdị mba ụwa kachasị elu dịka L'Oréal, Paris.
question: Kedu onye bụ onye isi ala France n'afọ 2022?

text: A mụrụ Maricela Gómez na Guayaquil na Nọvemba 23, 1976. Ọ malitere ọrụ ihe nkiri ya na mmalite afọ 1990 dị ka onye otu ụlọ ọrụ Teatro Bambalinas, nke onye na-eme ihe nkiri bụ Raúl Varela duziri. O mere ihe nkiri mbụ ya na telivishọn na 1993 dị ka onye mgbakwunye na telenovela "Ángel o Demonio" [es], nke Ecuavisa mepụtara. Nke a dugara na ọrụ na mmepụta ndị ọzọ dị ka "Dulce tormento" [es] (1995) na "María Soledad" [es] (1995).
question: Kedu mgbe amụrụ Maricela Gómez?
answer: A mụrụ Maricela Gómez na Nọvemba 23, 1976.

text: N'afọ 2018, Gómez gụsịrị akwụkwọ dị ka ọkà n'akparamàgwà mmadụ na Mahadum Guayaquil, na-enwetakwa onyinye Contenta nke ụlọ akwụkwọ ahụ. Ka ọ na-erule 2020, ọ hapụrụ ime ihe nkiri ma na-enye usoro ọgwụgwọ n'ịntanetị n'oge ọrịa COVID-19.

text: Abla al-Kahlawi (15 Disemba 1948 - 25 Jenụwarị 2021) bụ onye Ijipt ọkà mmụta na onye nkuzi nke ikpe okpukpe Alakụba, yana onye ndú okpukpe, onye nkwusa, na onye na-egosi televishọn. Ọ kụziri na Mahadum Al Azhar dị na Cairo, Egypt, ebe ọ bụ Dean nke ngalaba nke Islam na Arabic Studies na Koleeji umunwaanyi. E depụtara ya na mbipụta mmeghe nke The 500 Most Influential Muslims maka ọrụ ya na okpukpe na ụmụ nwanyị, n'afọ 2009, ma bipụta ọtụtụ ihe gbasara ụmụ nwanyị na ikpe okpukpe Alakụba. O kwusara ozi ọma n'Ijipt, n'onwe ya na telivishọn, yana na Saudi Arabia, ma kwusaa ozi ọma kwa ụbọchị ruo afọ abụọ na Masjid al-*aram, ụlọ alakụba kachasị mkpa nke Islam na Saudi Arabia, n'etiti 1987 na 1989.
question: Kedụ afọ Abla al-Kahlawi  nwetara nzere mmụta PhD?
answer: Abla al-Kahlawi nwetara nzere mmụta PhD n'afọ 1978.

answer: Ihe gburu Abla al-Kahlawi bụ COVID-19.
